# EmailJS Configuration
# Sign up at https://www.emailjs.com/ (free tier: 200 emails/month)
#
# 1. Create an email service (Gmail, Outlook, etc.)
# 2. Create TWO templates:
#    - Customer confirmation template (variables: to_email, to_name, service_name, booking_date, booking_time, booking_duration, booking_price, booking_id)
#    - Owner notification template (variables: to_email, customer_name, customer_email, customer_phone, service_name, booking_date, booking_time, booking_duration, booking_price, booking_id)
# 3. Copy your Service ID, Template IDs, and Public Key below

VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=
VITE_EMAILJS_CUSTOMER_TEMPLATE_ID=
VITE_EMAILJS_OWNER_TEMPLATE_ID=
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=

# Owner email for booking notifications
VITE_OWNER_EMAIL=gentlemens@barbershop.se
